# Internal working doc with real client names. Public version with
# anonymized signals lives in src/content/cases/ and in
# "[on] Public Portfolio 32-cases.md". This file must NEVER be tracked.
# (Square brackets escaped because [on] would otherwise match any of o,n.)
\[on\] Portfolio-Projects-by-business-theme.md

